Class TransactionManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.web3j.tx.TransactionManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientTransactionManager, RawTransactionManager, ReadonlyTransactionManager
    public abstract class TransactionManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Transaction manager abstraction for executing transactions with Ethereum client via various mechanisms.
